article.description: — TJ Starks scored 21 points as Cal State Northridge defeated Cal Poly 64-51 on Saturday.
article.headline: Starks scores 21 to lift CS Northridge past Cal Poly 64-51
article.linkText: Starks scores 21 to lift CS Northridge past Cal Poly 64-51
article.story: SAN LUIS OBISPO, Calif. -- — TJ Starks scored 21 points as Cal State Northridge defeated Cal Poly 64-51 on Saturday. Atin Wright had 14 points for Cal State Northridge (6-7, 2-4 Big West Conference), which ended its four-game losing streak. Darius Brown II added nine points and 11 rebounds. Alimamy Koroma had 13 points for the Mustangs (3-11, 1-7). Mark Crow added nine with four assists. Colby Rogers, the Mustangs’ second leading scorer at 10 points per game, had four on 2 of 11 shooting. Cal Poly defeated Cal State Northridge 76-70 on Friday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
